===Etymology===
From the Modern {{D.}} ''[[jacht]]'', from the {{OD.}} ''jagt'', short for ''[[jaghtschip]]'', (ship for chasing), from the verb ''[[jagen]]'', related to German ''[[jagen]]'' and Danish ''[[jage]]'' ('to hunt').

